常栖息在淡水湖沼区、池塘区或水田软泥土中，亦喜水流较平缓的河川河底{{r|shell_270}}。

==亞種==
* ''[[Cipangopaludina_fluminalis|Cipangopaludina fluminalis]]''{{r|Lu et al 2014}}

==寄生蟲==
本物種是是[[移睾棘口吸虫|移睾棘口吸虫]]的[[中間宿主|中間宿主]]<ref name="Chung 1999">{{Cite journal | last1 = Chung | first1 = P. R. | last2 = Jung | first2 = Y. | title = Cipangopaludina chinensis malleata (Gastropoda: Viviparidae): A new second molluscan intermediate host of a human intestinal fluke Echinostoma cinetorchis (Trematoda: Echinostomatidae) in Korea | journal = The Journal of Parasitology | volume = 85 | issue = 5 | pages = 963–964 | year = 1999 | pmid = 10577736 | doi=10.2307/3285837}}</ref>。

